channel.title: Installation ID???
channel.description:
Ok, I recently installed a new motherboard, and details aside I need to re-activate my version of windows (vista). So I phone up Microsoft and talk to their robot/[url='https://jbjensen.net/photos/MSoftTechSupportBombay.jpg']indian guy[/url] and both ask for an "Installation ID" which is 6 digits long, to continue. I have my vista key, and something called a product ID (neith of which are accepted), but nothing like installation ID. Has anyone else been through this? Or know where/what this install ID is? Much thanks.
God I hate tech support. :meh:
